
 Linkumori (Clear URLs) MV3 WebRequest Firefox Add-ons

The Linkumori codebase is primarily derived from other open-source projects, particularly the ClearURLs add-on and related projects.


SEE THIRD-PARTY-NOTICE FOLDER 
Which third party code has been used 

Due to constraints, later modifications are not tracked inline.
To view the full modification history, run:
  node linkumori-cli-tool.js

Then select "Generate Commit History". This will create a Markdown file